hopobject.body: I'd like to send this letter by fosamax femur mdl Just as the Pap smear has reduced cervical cancer rates by over 70 percent by finding and treating reversible pre-cancer before it becomes cancer, the goal of Atossa Genetics, maker of ForeCYTE and other diagnostic risk assessments, is to reduce the high rate of breast cancer through early detection of reversible precursor changes that can lead to breast cancer and to treat those early change. More information about determining your risk for breast cancer can be found at www.AtossaGenetics.com.
